@host = http://localhost:5143
@token = dummy-test-token

### Health check (no auth required)
GET {{host}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Discovery - list all discoverable event aliases
GET {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/discovery
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Schema Lookup - publication schema for trigger-imr-automate
GET {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/event-alias-schemas/trigger-imr-automate.v1-payload
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Schema Lookup - response schema (imr.completed)
GET {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/event-alias-schemas/imr.completed.v1-payload
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Schema Lookup - response schema (invoice.extracted)
GET {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/event-alias-schemas/invoice.extracted.v1-payload
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Publish - Request/Reply (trigger-imr-automate, requires recipient)
POST {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "eventAlias": "trigger-imr-automate.v1",
    "interactionType": "requestReply",
    "recipient": "my-automate-imr-process-named-0",
    "requestId": "req-001",
    "eventInteractionModel": {
        "eimId": "eim-imr-001"
    },
    "payload": {
        "documentId": "12345",
        "PO_Number": "PO-2026-001",
        "Vendor_Name": "Contoso Ltd."
    }
}

### Publish - Fire-and-Forget (trigger-some-automate)
POST {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "eventAlias": "trigger-some-automate.v1",
    "interactionType": "fireAndForget",
    "payload": {
        "patientType": "outpatient"
    }
}

### Publish - Request/Reply (invoice-data-extraction, recipient optional)
POST {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "eventAlias": "invoice-data-extraction.v1",
    "interactionType": "requestReply",
    "requestId": "req-002",
    "eventInteractionModel": {
        "eimId": "eim-invoice-001"
    },
    "payload": {
        "Invoice_Document": "99001",
        "PO_Number": "PO-2026-042",
        "Vendor_Name": "Fabrikam Inc."
    }
}

### Poll Responses - replace {requestId} with actual requestId from publish
# @name pollResponses
GET {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/requests/req-001/responses
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Poll Responses with afterSequence filter
GET {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/requests/req-001/responses?afterSequence=1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Error case - missing auth header
GET {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/discovery
Accept: application/json

### Error case - unknown event alias
POST {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "eventAlias": "nonexistent-alias",
    "interactionType": "fireAndForget",
    "payload": {}
}

### Schema Lookup - all-types-demo publication schema (exercises all 8 field types)
GET {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/event-alias-schemas/all-types-demo.v1-payload
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Schema Lookup - all-types success response schema
GET {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/event-alias-schemas/all-types.success.v1-payload
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Publish - Request/Reply (all-types-demo, exercises all 8 field types)
POST {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "eventAlias": "all-types-demo.v1",
    "interactionType": "requestReply",
    "requestId": "req-all-types-001",
    "eventInteractionModel": {
        "eimId": "eim-all-types-001"
    },
    "payload": {
        "PatientName": "Jane Doe",
        "DiagnosisCodes": ["ICD-10-A01", "ICD-10-B02"],
        "Priority": "High",
        "EncounterDate": "2026-04-17T14:30:00Z",
        "IsUrgent": true,
        "PageCount": 12,
        "ConfidenceScore": 0.87,
        "SourceDocument": "DOC-123456"
    }
}

### Poll Responses for all-types-demo (call 3 times to see completion)
GET {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/requests/req-all-types-001/responses
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Error case - unknown schema
GET {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/event-alias-schemas/nonexistent-schema
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Error case - unknown request for polling
GET {{host}}/api/cfs-events/v1/requests/nonexistent-request/responses
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
